(1, 1, '2012-04-09 08:05:17', '2012-04-09 08:05:17', 'Welcome to UK Boiler Quotes, a website setup to help save you both time and money whatever your boiler requirements. We provide boiler quotes throughout the UK on a daily basis from local, reputable boiler specialists eager to assist you.\r\n<a href="http://info4city.com/ukboiler/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/boiler.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-138" title="boiler" src="http://info4city.com/ukboiler/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/boiler.jpg" alt="" width="195" height="130" /></a>\r\n<div id="contentright2">\r\n\r\nWhether you’re looking to replace an old boiler with a new high-efficiency model, fit a brand new boiler system, get a boiler service or repair an existing boiler, our quotes will save you both time and money. What’s more they’re free, and come with no-obligation so there’s no risk in finding out how much money you can save!\r\n\r\nIf you would like to proceed with your <a href="http://www.ukboilerquotes.com/quote/">boiler quote</a>, simply click the quote button below, or you can find out further information by browsing this website.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div style="width: 100%;">\r\n<div style="width: 30%; float: left; text-align: center;">\r\n<div style="height: 40px;">Boiler Installaletion</div>\r\n<div><a href="http://info4city.com/ukboiler/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/boiler-installation.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-45" title="boiler-installation" src="http://info4city.com/ukboiler/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/boiler-installation.jpg" alt="" width="80%" /></a></div>\r\n<div style="width: 80%; text-align: justify;"><strong>Looking to save money on a new boiler installation? Find out how much important. you can save when looking for a new boiler, and reducing your boiler Installation Cost</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="width: 30%; float: left; text-align: center;">\r\n<div style="height: 40px;">Boiler Service</div>\r\n<div><a href="http://info4city.com/ukboiler/wp-content/