(7, 1, '2012-04-09 08:13:50', '2012-04-09 08:13:50', '<h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>\r\nWe’ve compiled a few of the most commonly requested questions we receive from our visitors below. If you would like to know any more about our website or boiler quote process please <a href="http://www.ukboilerquotes.com/contact/">contact us</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Are the quotes free?</strong> Yes, absolutely free. You pay nothing for using our service or for receiving the quotes. We take no commission for the work carried out, so the quotes are completely impartial.\r\n\r\n<strong>Do you publish our contact details online?</strong> No. We only present your contact details to a maximum of 5 companies in order to provide a quote. We never publish your details online, or show them to our whole network.\r\n\r\n<strong>Who receives my work requirements?</strong> Our industry leading network of boiler tradesmen are given your work requirements based on your work requirements and geographical area.\r\n\r\n<strong>Are the quotes you provide delivered online?</strong> No. To ensure total accuracy, the quotes will be delivered by the persons wishing to carry out the work.\r\n\r\n<strong>How many quotes will I receive?</strong> A maximum of five. We will allow a limit of five companies access to your contact details. In the unlikely event that we cannot find any tradesmen to quote for your job, you will be notified via email within 6 days.', 'FAQ''s', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'quotes', '', '', '2012-04-09 11:08:35', '2012-04-09 11:08:35', '', 0, 'http://info4city.com/ukboiler/?page_id=7', 3, 'page', '', 0),
