(139, 1, '2012-04-10 08:56:11', '2012-04-10 08:56:11', 'Welcome to UK Boiler Quotes, a website setup to help save you both time and money whatever your boiler requirements. We provide boiler quotes throughout the UK on a daily basis from local, reputable boiler specialists eager to assist you.\r\n<a href="http://info4city.com/ukboiler/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/boiler.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-37 alignleft" title="boiler" src="http://info4city.com/ukboiler/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/boiler.jpg" alt="" width="195" height="130" /></a>\r\n<div id="contentright2">\r\n\r\nWhether you’re looking to replace an old boiler with a new high-efficiency model, fit a brand new boiler system, get a boiler service or repair an existing boiler, our quotes will save you both time and money. What’s more they’re free, and come with no-obligation so there’s no risk in finding out how much money you can save!\r\n\r\nIf you would like to proceed with your <a href="http://www.ukboilerquotes.com/quote/">boiler quote</a>, simply click the quote button below, or you can find out further information by browsing this website.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div style="width: 100%;">\r\n<div style="width: 30%; float: left; text-align: center;"><div style="height:40px;">Boiler Installaletion</div>\r\n<div><a href="http://info4city.com/ukboiler/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/boiler-installation.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-45" title="boiler-installation" src="http://info4city.com/ukboiler/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/boiler-installation.jpg" alt="" width="80%" /></a></div>\r\n<div style="width: 80%; text-align: justify;"><strong>Looking to save money on a new boiler installation? Find out how much important. you can save when looking for a new boiler, and reducing your boiler Installation Cost</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="width: 30%; float: left; text-align: center;">\r\n<div style="height:40px;">Boiler Service</div>\r\n<div><a href="http://info4city.com/ukboiler/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/boiler-service.jpg"><img class="alignright size-full wp-image-77" title="boiler-service" src="http://info4city.com/ukboiler/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/boiler-service.jpg" alt="" width="80%" /></a></div>\r\n<div style="width: 80%; float: right; text-align: justify;"><strong>Looking to save money on a new boiler installation? Find out how much important. you can save when looking for a new boiler, and reducing your boiler Installation Cost</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="width: 30%; float: right; text-align: center;">\r\n<div style="height:35px;">Boiler Repair</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://info4city.com/ukboiler/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/boiler-repair5.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-84" title="boiler-repair" src="http://info4city.com/ukboiler/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/boiler-repair5.jpg" alt="" width="80%" /></a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="width: 80%; float: right; text-align: justify;"><strong>Looking to save money on a new boiler installation? Find out how much important. you can save when looking for a new boiler, and reducing your boiler Installation Cost</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="width: 100%; float: left;">\r\n<h2>UK Boiler Scrappage Scheme</h2>\r\n<strong><strong>The UK Boiler Scrappage Scheme began in 2010 and attempted to incentivise people to upgrade from G-grade boilers to high-efficiency A-grade boilers. Though the scheme has now ended there is still a lot of money to be saved with a new boiler</strong> </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong> <strong></strong><strong> <strong><strong></strong></strong>\r\n</strong><a href="http://info4city.com/ukboiler/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/boiler-efficiency2.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-98" title="boiler-efficiency" src="http://info4city.com/ukboiler/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/boiler-efficiency2.jpg" alt="" width="195" height="150" /></a>The scheme proved so popular across the UK that all of the allocated tokens have been used up, and nearly 120,000 boilers have been replaced to more energy-efficient models. It is possible however, to still save significant amounts of money on a new boiler installation across the UK. Click below to find out how:\r\n</strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Boiler Quotes', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1-revision-67', '', '', '2012-04-10 08:56:11', '2012-04-10 08:56:11', '', 1, 'http://info4city.com/ukboiler/?p=139', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
